summaries.short: In this exclusive podcast, Rose Cranberry uncovers eye-opening details about the disappearance of LaToya Thompson.
summaries.full: When 26 year-old LaToya Thompson went missing, Rose Cranberry hopped right on the case. In this exclusive podcast episode of Looking for LaToya, Rose conducts additional interviews with the people who knew LaToya best, talks to new witnesses, and uncovers additional eye-opening details about her disappearance. Starring Terri J. Vaughn, SZA, Porsha Williams, Ray J, and more.
